title: Windows XP PRO SP3 CORP 5503
description:
Windows XP Professional SP3 5503
No activation needed.
No crack needed.
Passes all WGA checks - fully updateable
key: V2C47-MK7JD-3R89F-D2KXW-VPK3J

SP3 has a broken IE6 by default. To fix this, run the IE6 Crash Fix on
the CD.
    
Burn this image at 8x or slower speed to ensure a proper install. When
doing a new install, be sure to do a FULL format of your hard-drive.
QUICK format will almost always give errors at install. If you have more
than one optical drive, you may need to install from the SLAVE drive.
